data.description: If you’ve been searching for the ease of main level living in a tranquil setting at an INCREDIBLE VALUE, welcome home! This incredibly warm and inviting 1.5 story home backs to the 9th fairway in Lakewood! With soaring vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light, this home manages to feel both open and cozy at the same time. Perfect for entertaining or quiet family time with an oversized great room featuring a floor-to-ceiling fireplace that opens to a gleaming kitchen with quartz countertops, subway tile backsplash, white cabinets, slate flooring and stainless appliances. And a spacious dining room offers extra seating options for all your larger gatherings. A spacious primary suite with walk in closet and open, updated euro-style bath! A second bedroom, full bath and laundry are also on the main level for the ultimate convenience. Upstairs you’ll find a private 3rd bedroom and full bath, along with a large cedar closet for extra storage. Want more? Head to the finished lower level where you'll find a large family room with fantastic LVP flooring, a non-conforming bedroom and full bath, plus a bonus room that makes for great office, gaming or hobby space. All that and still tons of unfinished storage space! Newer windows (2019), Furnace/AC (2018), Gutters/Downspouts (2018). New Water Heater (2022), Refrigerator(2022). Don’t forget to check out all the amenities that make Lakewood the perfect community to live and play, including two lakes, community pool, tennis courts and clubhouse.
